173 A.3d 598 NATIONSTAR MORTGAGE, LLC, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. IRINA IUDINA, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER, AND VASLILY VYPRYATHKIN, AND BANK OF AMERICA, N.A., DEFENDANTS.

C-304 September Term 2017

079935 November 14, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002993-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
